				</p>

				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Contact</h2>
				<p>
					For questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@variscout.com" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">hello@variscout.com</a>.
				</p>
				<p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">
					RDMAIC Oy — Helsinki, Finland
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
